The paper discusses the analysis of textual data in software projects, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions natural language processing (cs.CL), automatic text analysis (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG) as methods used for text analysis. Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of dealing with large amounts of textual data, which could fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
